{
  "3094480": {
    "name": "烂奶酪 (Bad Cheese)",
    "steam_appid": 3094480,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/345a5f7bb0f167a4608de285a64790fd.avif?t=1764984941\" width=616 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将化身为一只小老鼠，当母亲不在家的时候，与不太称职的父亲共同度过周末。请表现出你最听话的一面，让父亲心情愉快。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/2e57e653fd59d17fc937269ef7b29669.webp?t=1764984941\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/4985e539107367de84706158fd7ce9fc.poster.avif?t=1764984941\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/4985e539107367de84706158fd7ce9fc.webm?t=1764984941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/4985e539107367de84706158fd7ce9fc.mp4?t=1764984941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你和你的父亲、母亲、兄长同住一个屋檐下，面临着种种问题。尽量不要惹麻烦，以免遭受惩罚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/27e28f32d4f35e55da74e0f1569c4e9b.webp?t=1764984941\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/6e8781af5e7612511c3c75924cf7bae6.poster.avif?t=1764984941\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/6e8781af5e7612511c3c75924cf7bae6.webm?t=1764984941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/6e8781af5e7612511c3c75924cf7bae6.mp4?t=1764984941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >擦洗、扫地、清洁、炸薯条、消灭蜘蛛、给爸爸拿药——总而言之，做一个好孩子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/d1f34df329feb3cb4ca2c93add4ec2d8.webp?t=1764984941\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/e50c5762db860bd791fd140e5e0ab8b6.poster.avif?t=1764984941\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/e50c5762db860bd791fd140e5e0ab8b6.webm?t=1764984941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/e50c5762db860bd791fd140e5e0ab8b6.mp4?t=1764984941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索房子，寻找散落在各处的零食和玩具手办。这可能是住在家里的唯一乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/27610b38b70837173f871d19ceb878e6.webp?t=1764984941\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/9b9da384624d45610651468f15c76566.poster.avif?t=1764984941\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/9b9da384624d45610651468f15c76566.webm?t=1764984941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/9b9da384624d45610651468f15c76566.mp4?t=1764984941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在房子的不同区域直面种种困境，体验一只老鼠宝宝努力在不正常的家庭中维持正常生活的残酷现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094480/extras/77e7bd78a7d5d184809e903fcd059288.webp?t=1764984941\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p>",
